data.description: Welcome to this charming 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo nestled in the desirable Brittany Highlands community of Aurora, CO. This home boasts a beautifully updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, creating a gourmet culinary experience. Enjoy the comfort of central air conditioning and cozy up by the wood-burning fireplace during the colder months. The community offers a refreshing pool for hot summer days, and the convenience of being close to multiple shopping centers ensures that all your retail and dining needs are just moments away. This is the perfect opportunity to experience modern living in a convenient and welcoming neighborhood.   Set your showing as this one won't last long!!
